InstaLIVE with @amitagadre on Food and Nutrition when you travel 🧳✈️🍱👅

We covered questions like-
- How do you eat healthy when you travel and not come back with extra weight or lose fitness?
- How to make smarter choices at airports/on flights/when there aren’t too many options?
- How to try all kinds of food when you travel but avoid weight gain?
- Which indulgences should you give in to?
- Getting adequate protein when you are on the go
- Coffee, meal preps, meal timings, mindful eating, maintaining gut health and SO much more! 🤌🏼✨
